{
  "stem": "12666.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And all the pilots did obey the order, but there was one major who refused to wear them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "So he held out for a whole month.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "We knew he was a political commissar.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] But later on, sheepishly, he put them on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] That was also another incident in Alaska we had.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "It was very interesting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But then, after I got out of Alaska, my mother had an operation, and I had to get a job.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I went to Washington, DC, shopping around and contacting my friends.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they say, look, they need linguists at the Nuremberg war crime trials.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why don't you apply for that?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Again, I'm going to ask you, can put this in time perspective for me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How long were you in Alaska?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Until '45, when the war was over.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When-- after victory in Europe, and after victory in Japan.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because when victory in Europe happened, they mobilized us and they told us that we are going to go to Siberia, to the city of [INAUDIBLE] to be interpreters there, because Japan had to be defeated.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the Soviet Union did declare war on Japan.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I didn't look forward to go to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When I hear the words of Siberia, its kind of-- [LAUGHS] but fortunately, right away, VJ Day happened.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then we were able to be discharged [LAUGHS] in '45.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Applied for a job.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
